" Colorscheme {{{
syntax enable
colorscheme badwolf
" }}}

" Spaces and Tabs {{{
set tabstop=4	" Number of visual spaces per tab when reading
set softtabstop=4	" Number of spaces in tab when editing
set expandtab	" tabs are now just spaces. Helpful for languages like python where spaces are the norm
set modelines=1
set autoindent
filetype indent on
filetype plugin on
" }}}

